            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-4">
            <a href="#" class="">
              <img src="http://placehold.it/150x150" class = "pull-right" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="tab-pane fade" id="discussions">
        <div class="media">
          <a class="pull-left" href="#">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
          </a>
          <div class="media-body">
            <h4 class="media-heading">Clammy hand</h4>
            Every time I attend events from this club my hands fall off. <br>
            <small>Posted by Nigel, 17/3/2014 at 3:00am</small>
